WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.440
You're part of the world's top skilled trade network where quality is key.

00:00:04.840 --> 00:00:08.080
Ongoing learning is required through field work and videos.

00:00:08.440 --> 00:00:13.320
Our video library includes system and quality guides to help direct you when needed.

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:15.720
These are accessible at all times.

00:00:16.040 --> 00:00:18.360
New videos will be added regularly.

00:00:18.680 --> 00:00:23.360
If a required video is available, it must be watched before accessing the app.

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:29.560
Some role specific videos will include short tests that must be passed before the app is unlocked.

00:00:29.959 --> 00:00:32.640
You will always know when you have new videos to watch.

00:00:32.879 --> 00:00:39.239
The app will lock except for the system quality guide icon, which shows a notification for new tasks.

00:00:39.519 --> 00:00:42.160
Click the icon to see what you need to watch or do.

00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:48.000
We'll keep you updated on everything field and system related to ensure quality and understanding.

